text: Ban mian is quite yummy with a thick soup base at $4.

Bought dinner Century Egg Minced Pork Porridge to pack home. Am surprised that it tasted good. Seen that they sell other dishes too. Now this has picked my interest to try other dishes.  Am so coming back!!!

Delicious and comforting bowl of fish soup with Egg Noodles. The fried fish is very succulent, batter is not thick, it's well done with good flavor. Sliced white fish is very fresh. Service is excellent. The egg noodles is also very well cooked, noodles are just nice and not soggy.
Good fish soup and Ban mian. I like that they give more vegetables too.
